NHL Game Content

nhl_game_content.Rd

Returns game content for a given game ID

nhl_game_content(game_id)

Arguments

game_id

Game unique ID

Value

Returns a tibble

Examples

# \donttest{
  nhl_game_content(game_id=2021020182)
